tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE errors (
  error_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  error_message TEXT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE debugging (
  debug_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  debug_info TEXT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE training (
  training_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  training_data TEXT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE errors (
    error_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    error_description TEXT,
    error_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE debug_info (
    debug_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    neural_network_id INT,
    debug_message TEXT,
    debug_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE training_logs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    neural_network_id INT,
    log_message TEXT,
    log_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE training_data (
    data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    training_set_name TEXT,
    data_description TEXT,
    data_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE neural_network_logs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    log_type VARCHAR,
    error_message TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE training_iterations (
    iteration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    training_loss FLOAT,
    validation_loss FLOAT,
    iteration_time FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE model_parameters (
    parameter_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    parameter_name VARCHAR,
    parameter_value FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE network_layers (
    layer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    layer_name VARCHAR,
    activation_function VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE training_metrics (
    metric_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    metric_name VARCHAR,
    metric_value FLOAT
)
